The dipstick normally would bottom out but there is a bump on the plate underneath it to allow it to clear:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts4/109-DipstickLength.jpg
http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts4/110-SumpPlate.jpg

The length you are looking for is basically the length of the dipstick.

The original marks are at these locations:

